Detailed Description

template<class SetsType>
class Tatree< SetsType >

Template class representing a trie data structure (this is an "interface" of the Tatre_base class).

This class differs from the mother class Tatree_base by providing additional methods and the access to a more complete iterator. Using this class, it is possible to explore all the sets stored in trie using the iterators ++. The template parameter is the type of the element stored in the trie.
